<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.1.9">
<l>kumpamiku matayāṉai pākaṉoṭuṅ kulaintuviḻa</l>
<l>kompataṉaip paṟitteṟinta kūttaṉamarn tuṟaiyumiṭam</l>
<l>vampaviḻuñ ceṇpakattiṉ maṇaṅkamaḻum nāṅkaitaṉṉuḷ</l>
<l>cempoṉmatiḷ poḻilpuṭaicūḻ tiruttēva ṉārtokaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place where serenely dwells the dancer who, when he defeated</l>
<l>The elephant with temples great with musth and the driver,</l>
<l rend="indent">so they fell, having plucked out the tusks, hurled [them],</l>
<l>Is Tiruttēvaṉārtokai in Nāṅkai, surrounded on [all] sides by groves,</l>
<l rend="indent">walled with rose gold,</l>
<l>Where wafts the scent of champaka which unfurls fragrance.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
